race.comment: SUPREME THUNDER (1) continues to leave himself with too much to do but has been savaging the line. Drops back to a sprinting trip off 7 weeks in-between and is sure to be coming late again. ARTISSI (10) was unlucky not to return a winner at Kingscote when beaten a head. Backs up quickly and is sure to have come on from that but will need to overcome the wide alley. AMBELLO (2) is another who lacks early muster but will appreciate the drop in grade. Will settle back early again but if the gap appears he can give them a scare. MISS GATSBY (12) was better last time when sticking on gamely into the frame at Penola. Hasn't won for a very long time but is going well enough to find the frame.
